name: Structural Vibration by erikaart
description:
Bars that support and elevate, divide and unite in a single piece, capable of holding a universe of emotions and desires, vibrating to the sound that you decide and want to feel.
Work created on June 25, 2021.
Digital in Photoshop, variety of brushes and effects.
"This work may not be reproduced commercially."
Grateful for acquiring my work, my talent to satisfy your world.
